\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 and each 
\begin_inset Formula $y\in\left\{ 1,\ldots,k\right\} $
\end_inset

, we want to produce a probability where 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{y=1}^{k}\theta_{y}=1$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

